| `pkg/controller/trustmanager/controller.go` | Add `proxyInformer` field to `Reconciler`, accept in `New()`, add RBAC marker, add imports |
| `pkg/controller/trustmanager/deployments.go` | Add `updateProxyEnv` method, call it from `getDeploymentObject`, add `Env` to `containerModified` |

## Commands to run

```bash
# 1. Regenerate CRD manifests and deepcopy (picks up the new RBAC marker)
make update

# 2. Verify the code compiles
make build

# 3. Run unit tests
make test
```

No new files are created. The `make update` target regenerates RBAC ClusterRole manifests from the kubebuilder markers (the new `config.openshift.io proxies` get/list/watch permission will be added to the generated role). `make build` and `make test` verify compilation and existing tests pass.
